return {title = "Little Horn", id = 503, description = {'The chance to for each tear to become a void tear is affected by your luck stat and at +15 Luck it will activate 20% of the time', 'While firing tears you have a 5% chance to fire a void tear, that will instantly kill any non-boss enemy it comes into contact with', 'REPENTANCE - The visual effect was changed on this. Instead of just killing the enemy Big Horn now appears and grabs them, instantly killing them. Tears are no longer piercing', 'Isaac also grows a horn on his head, which causes you to deal contact damage to enemies by running into them (this effect deals base damage of 3.5 per tick)', 'Void tears from this item can also destroy blue/purple fires, spiked blocks and stone grimaces'}}